<div id="comment_244752661" class="brown_comment">
  <div class="xhr_comment_photo">
    	<a alt="Lori Keeton" href="/user/show/17557841-lori-keeton"><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1371329305p1/17557841.jpg" alt="17557841" /></a>
  </div>
  <div class="xhr_comment_body">
    <a style="font-weight:bold" href="/user/show/17557841-lori-keeton">Lori Keeton</a>

      
<span id="freeTextContainer4389027929519932592">Kathleen, you have written a perfect review which mirrors the easy writing style of Maugham. I appreciate your insights into how Maugham plays his par</span>
  <span id="freeText4389027929519932592" style="display:none">Kathleen, you have written a perfect review which mirrors the easy writing style of Maugham. I appreciate your insights into how Maugham plays his part in the novel. It makes perfect sense and worked very well. Fabulous review!</span>
